name: Womens Big Jugs Baby Tee or Tank
description:
We are unable to picture both shirts and this price is for one of the following...

The women's tee shirt is a high quality "baby tee" fit black shirt with white screening.  It features the Big Jugs logo over the appropriate area with the words "Dirty Country Music" under it.

The girls tank top is a white "boy beater" cut with a black Big Jugs logo over the appropriate area with the words "Dirty Country Music" under it.  this is our most popular selling shirt!

name: Mens- Big Jug Shirt
description:
Our original shirt logo brought back by popular demand for a 2010 run!  

It features a large jug in the middle with the words "Since Long Ago, 101 Proof at the top and "Ass Kickin' Blend" in the center.   The bottom has the words "Bottled in Santa Barbara, CA."

Black shirt with white screening.  Single pass screening for "vintage look."

name: No Shame Tour Shirt 2010
description:
This was our shirt that was made for the 2010 "No Shame Tour."  It was made in limited quantities and we aren't printing any more when they are gone, so get 'em while they are hot!

Black shirt with a frame surrounding the image of a bull rider taming a well nourished woman.  Below the image reads "2010 NO SHAME TOUR."

If you are able to choose a size below, then we got it.  If not, we are out.

Black shirt, single screened  white image for a "vintage look".

name: Big Jugs- Ridin' Dirty *Signed*
description:
Big Jugs first release in 2008.  It contains 12 tracks of knee stompin', hell raisin' ditties sure to get the neighbors offended.

Exclusive to this site...
All copies of the cd will be signed by all current members!

Members: Alouishious, Leeroy Dynamite, General Sherman, Eugene Burlap, Vegas Washington, Woodburn Burnwood

name: Big Jugs- It's OK *Signed*
description:
This 6 song EP was released in June 2010 on Stroke Records.  It is Big Jugs sophomore release and has 30 minutes of punchy, raunchy bargrass and drunkytonk country music.  It was tracked over a three night bender in The Den of Inequity Studios in Las Vegas.  Destined to be a classic. 

Exclusive to this site...  All copies will be signed by all current members of the band  

Members: Alouishious, The Deacon, Leeroy Dynamite, Vegas Washington, Woodburn Burnwood
